=== HIGH ===

[HIGH] EC2-001 — Security group allows unrestricted ingress
  Resource: sg-1 (EC2)
  Remediation: Restrict security group ingress to specific CIDR blocks.

[HIGH] S3-002 — S3 bucket encryption not configured
  Resource: bucket-1 (S3)
  Remediation: Enable SSE-S3 or SSE-KMS encryption on the bucket.

=== WARNING ===

[WARNING] S3-001 — S3 bucket versioning not enabled
  Resource: bucket-1 (S3)
  Remediation: Enable versioning on the S3 bucket.

=== INFO ===

[INFO] LAMBDA-001 — Lambda function environment variables may contain secrets
  Resource: func-1 (Lambda)
  Remediation: Use AWS Secrets Manager or Parameter Store for sensitive values.

